downloadTitle: Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012 R3 One-time Vendors and Invoices Sample CSV File
downloadDescription: Sample CSV file, linked to from Dynamics AX Help "Import and create one-time vendors" topic.
detailsSection: CSV file contains sample Accounts Payable data for fictitious vendors and invoices.  Users can create their own files and import into Dynamics Ax 2012 R3 CU8.
systemRequirementsSection: • For information about the system requirements for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012, see System requirements for Microsoft Dynamics AX 2012.
installInstructionSection:
1. Click Download to download the document.
  2. Save the file to your computer.
